<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .logo{
          border-radius: 50%;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
        }
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .content {
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .otp-code {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/006/547/178/non_2x/creative-modern-abstract-ecommerce-logo-design-colorful-gradient-online-shopping-bag-logo-design-template-free-vector.jpg" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>OTP Verification</h2>
            <p>Dear <%=name%>,</p>
            <p>Thank you for choosing GadgetGalaxy. Use the following OTP to complete your sign-up procedures. The OTP is valid for 5 minutes.</p>
            <div class="otp-code"><%=otp%></div>
            <p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 GadgetGalaxy. . All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
